The Keys to Your Heart
You are attracted to those who are unbridled, untrammeled, and free. In love, you feel the most alive when your lover is creative and never lets you feel bored. You'd like to your lover to think you are stylish and alluring. You would be forced to break up with someone who was ruthless, cold-blooded, and sarcastic. Your ideal relationship is lasting. You want a relationship that looks to the future... one you can grow with. Your risk of cheating is low. Even if you're tempted, you'd try hard not to do it. You think of marriage as something precious. You'll treasure marriage and treat it as sacred. In this moment, you think of love as something you can get or discard anytime. You're feeling self centered.
What Are The Keys To Your Heart?
How to make a nghtlildevil160 Ingredients: 5 parts anger 5 parts courage 1 part energy Method: Combine in a tall glass half filled with crushed ice. Add a little fitness if desired! Meow! Your Birthdate: December 16 You're incredibly introverted and introspective. You live inside your head. You spend a lot of alone time meditating and thinking. People see you as withdrawn, and at times they are right. You are caring and deep, but it may be difficult for you to show this side of yourself. Your strength: Your original approach to thinking Your weakness: You tend to shy away from others Your power color: Pale blue Your power symbol: Wavy line Your power month: July
Your Hidden Talent
You have the power to persuade and influence others.
You're the type of person who can turn a whole room around.
The potential for great leadership is there, as long as you don't abuse it.
Always remember, you have a lot more power over people than you might think!
What's Your Hidden Talent?

So I had this really messed up dream. Anybody on what it means? Any ideas on meaning please let me know, I'm stumped.

<lj-cut>
 So starts out with the weird ceromony of Hailee's birthday (yes I'm sorry you were in this, kyle too..) So on this brithday  a grand ritual happens of having to shot with an arrow the bottom out of this little basket, several guys try to do it and the one that succeeds is your lover. So yours happens and it was Kyle and you were both happy as can be. 
 Jumps to the next day, my brithday. I have to do this but I didn't know the full extent of the ritual so I just do it to the guy I want's basket and call it he won. When he comes over, I tell him. We are madly in love, and he kisses me. Oh for a dream it was one damn good kiss, ohhhh.. (lol)  
 Jump..So he's supposed to go to this family thing with me. But when I get all excited about it and is talking to Mr. Dine about it. He says he's having one, and suddenly my Mom decides shes gonna have hers with Mr. Dines and my bf was invited. It was a hoax to split us up. My bf runs away to be depressed cause he can't have me, but I eventually find him at the bottom of a pool hiding. So I dove down there, brought him up and talked with him. Telling him how much I loved him. So we decided to run away together. In order to do this though we have to hide away in Hailee's Basement for a little while. (Why? I have no idea)Her dad almost catches us, So we sneak off. Running down steps and jumping this, having a great time. 
 When suddenly we are a cruise ship, stowing away or stealing it I couldn't tell. Felt like I was stealing it, but we were running around and hiding from people, and starving. So more like stowing away, but ne ways the people on the ship wanted to find out despertatly. As we were hiding out. We ran aruound for a while, but we get hungry. So we steal some stuff and end up with enough to buy corn. (corn??) We go to a room to be alone and jsut talk and have our corn delivered. Only this is a suite and it happens tons of poeple are in it, we didn't mind. We just asked if we could use their balacony for a minute. The lady responded with her and her bf were leaving for a bit and didn't mind too much but as not to mess anything up. So we order the corn and suddenly we hear the gaurds coming. Scared we couldn't tell if they were coming from upstairs or down, so we go back and forth. Then we choose up stairs but get scared half way up and do down. The guards caught us, ends up The lady said we could use her balacony so she could catch us. It was her cruise ship and she was pissed. 
 Jump..I walk into a probahtion office, a gaurd standing on duty. Serveral people standing talk to me as I'm for some reason famous for my cruise stunt or something. Ne ways a friend of mine is working and tells me he needs to talk to me. So he takes me back in some bedroom, and wants me to help him steal somethiong of willy wonkas that really looks like something of the cat in the hats. We shut the door, alerting the guard until he comes looking to see whats going on. My friend and I chat for a while, and the gaurd comes in and tells us we have to leave teh room. 

End of dream..wow what a dream, but that kiss ohh lol
</lj-cut>

Ok I don't know what Al's problem is today but honestly he needs to grow up. Ok, hes sleeping on the couch in the Living room with Mom and Sammy. I get a phone call (that happens I think not even once a month) and answer it and continue the conversation I had with her where we had left off from earlier. Al waits a minute or two and insists Sam gets on the phone and answers. (I was in the kitchen) I hear her say hi, and I'm like ok whats are you doing? So I walk over there and ask her what shes doing? She looks scared, and Als all like I thought it was her mom. I'm like well if it was her mom wouldn't I have brought the phone in there and said her sam its your mom. Instead of just talking like I am. So I finish cooking and talking on the phone, and tell everyone to come eat. Mom calls Al in and he comes after wandering around for a bit, he sits down and starts a huge fight over why I jumped on Sam about being the phone. I'm like well I get a phone once in a while, and if it was for her I would have told you. No one told you it had to be her, and you had to invade my phone call. And he went on and on about I should use my cell phone, and well in order to use my cell phone it has to be on the speaker phone, so I get less privacy than I would on the house phone. He keeps yelling cause I "jumped" all over sam. WELL, IM NOT THE FUCKING ONE THAT INSISTED IT WAS HER MOM AND FOR HER TO GET ON THE PHONE, NOW AM I? ROAR!! Mom understood, and told him just to go to bed, he didn't. Ya know I really hate about him, is he thinks hes always fucking right, and throws a fit about me when I think I'm right and try to tell him hes wrong cause ya know hes never wrong. Mom has this problem too. Ya know if he it was her mom I would have told her, don't know why he had to think it was. Ya think he just coulda stayed outta it?!

I went to work, only I worked at a shopping center / pool area. A friend of mine from Wendy's worked there, her names Jen. When at work we liked to hang out a lot, so thats what we were doing. Only some how it jumps ( I don't know how) to her being a prostitute, and already helping some guy out in the pool. I couldn't believe it, but she urged me on to join her, as he had a friend and he need a prostitute too. So I jumped it, and became one to. I had a condem, I opened it and put it on him and off we were in the pool. I didn't actually see any of the uhh sex part, it skipped to being in the shopping center just walking around. Now I'm a full prostitute only its at work too, wierd. A bunch of big shots come in, that need prostitutes, and  only center people will do. When I'm picked to do it, I jump for joy and celebrate. I get in the pool and we do it again. Again I see no sex, not even the condem this time. It again jumps to me walking around in the shopping center. I run in the Jen yet again, and she said she'd be in the pool and someone was there waiting for me. (They had asked for me personally) So realizing I didn't have a condem with me, tell my manager I'm leaving for a minute and will be right back. I go to find a cvs or something for one, but I find I'm just in my neighborhood (weird, cause I'm in South Carolina presently) I run around the block searching for a store or someone to ask and I come across a bunch of guys and ask for one. Reassuring they do, and don't mind just giving it to me. I rush back to the pool and come across that the guy wanting me was in fact my ex-boyfriend. (Jesse) I'm shocked and just kinda stand there staring him. He looks at me and says I'm not here for me, I want help for my nephew (some pre-teen kid.) He goes on to say that he wanted to help him but didn't want just anyone, but thought I'd be best. So I say ok, and get him in the pool so that I could uhh "help him" Before I even finish getting the condem out of the package, the kid starts freaking out. I'm stunned don't know whats going on. The kid is screaming not to touch his ass, and no ones around and I've got both hands on the condem package. He screams again and jumps out of the pool, with something like a dildo sticking out of his ass. I'm shocked, I look up at Jesse and find that he had done it, and had already been out of the pool. They walk away together, after Jesse gives me a look of disappoint and disgrace. I'm left there shocked and what happened, and soon to be crying. Everyone around me staring, thinking I had hurt that boy, I knew that Jesse had killed my career and my life. I don't know what to do, he had adverently sabotted (sp) me, even Jen wanted notihng to do with me. 
</lj-cut>
